nk.sbstck.com/redirect/76f23ec2-34a2-48a7-99bc-bb12371fe453?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXA=
wZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]
I=E2=80=99m a long time Slack [ https://link.sbstck.com/redirect/76f23ec2-3=
4a2-48a7-99bc-bb12371fe453?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXep=
KbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] fan. This piece on Slack in 2020 [ https://link.sbstck=
=2Ecom/redirect/b94ee0f9-374a-4962-8cb=
9-0dc5ba5371a3?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.g=
b8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] was one of my first viral essa=
ys ever. Three years and tens of thousands of Slack messages later, and I=
=E2=80=99m more bullish on Slack than ever. And I=E2=80=99m not alone. Slac=
k is where millions of companies =E2=80=93 of varying sizes =E2=80=93 get w=
ork done.
We all know that everyday tasks can slow you and your team down
Back-and-forth emails. Meetings on top of meetings. A never-ending to-do li=
st.=C2=A0But Slack is the single space to connect with everything, share an=
d search for information, and help your teams do more with less. And with S=
lack Pro [ https://link.sbstck.com/redirect/76f23ec2-34a2-48a7-99bc-bb12371=
fe453?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ],=
 you can:
