make decisions and move work forward. Crtl+f makes the world go round.
Connect instantly with huddles
Fun fact, Dan and I have never scheduled a video meeting. But we huddle all=
 the time. With huddles you can talk, video chat, or share your screen inst=
antly with anyone in your Slack.
