an>There&#8217;s a reason that they were able to succeed despite that, and =
it&#8217;s not just the brilliance of the product. It&#8217;s the fact that=
 Airbnb seemed like a terrible idea! Airbnb had a really hard time raising =
money. It faced </span><a href=3D"https://link.sbstck.com/redirect/1e9385cc=
-c7d2-43d9-974a-37d9eeacd151?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXX=
