 $1.5 billion valuation.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64)=
; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Because of how h=
ard it is to build what Runway&#8217;s built, and the fact that it only rec=
ently became apparent that it was possible, it&#8217;s been protected by No=
velty Uncertainty to date. They&#8217;ve also shipped products at a rapid c=
lip to stay ahead. I&#8217;m not sure that the company has real moats yet, =
though, and it should act quickly to dig them before uncertainty runs out.&=
#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: =
26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>This is why strategy is important for star=
